<HEADLINE>
THE RELIGIOUS RIGHT MAY BE A GENUINE VOTING BLOC AGAIN 
</HEADLINE>
   (Commentary)  
 &HT;    
 &HT;    (To purchase this ``separate buy'' article from the New York
Times Syndicate please contact syndicate sales representative DEBRA
WEYDERT at 732-390-4480)
 &HT;    
 By DIANA BUTLER BASS  
 (Distributed by New York Times Special Features)  
 &HT;    
 &HT;    
 &HT;    Last autumn the evangelical magazine ``Christianity Today''
posed the cover-story question: ``Is the Religious Right
