ambitious and wondrously imaginative new 10-hour miniseries,
beginning Sunday. ``Kingdom'' re-imagines all of the classic fairy
tales, but in a modern context, with humor, suspense, special
effects and plenty of Freudian meat. Truly worth watching. Grade:
A-. (Kloer, Atlanta Journal-Constitution). 22.
