Confidential''). The Oscar-winning actor talks about making the
comedy movie, his new-found affection for Atlanta (he recently
visited The Carter Center here in his work for the U.N.) and about
his engagement to Catherine Zeta-Jones (plus, he reveals the
pick-up line he used on her when they first met). (BLongino,
