Charles Stein. 800 words.
</P>
<P>
   &UR; SPORTS &LR;   &UR; (s) &LR;
</P>
<P>
   HKN-BRUINS-SINDEN (Edmonton, Alberta) _ Harry Sinden says the
Bruins support the NHL's decision to suspend defenseman Marty
McSorley through the playoffs. By Nancy Marrapese-Burrell. 650
words.
</P>
<P>
   BBA-REDSOX-OLEARY (Fort Myers, Fla.) _ The skeptics, says Troy
O'Leary, are already predicting doom and gloom for the Red Sox,
despite last season's success. By Gordon Edes. 950 words.
</P>
