and the S&AMP;P 500 down 19 points while the Nasdaq composite index was
up 2 points. Treasury prices are modestly higher. European stock
markets were also lower: London was down 0.38 percent and Frankfurt
down 1.02 percent. The Nikkei closed up 0.27 percent, while the
