 ART ADV.: Photos with WOMEN-ICE, CHILDCARE-COLUMN and
MIT-SPORTS-LAB are being transmitted to NYT Photo Service
subscribers.  
 For Immediate Release  
 
<TEXT>
<P>
   The Boston Globe plans to move the following FEATURE stories for
use by NYTimes News Service clients.
</P>
