   VENTURE-CAPITAL _ ATLANTA _ Advance on next week's high-powered
Red Herring venture capital conference. About 50 companies will
come to the Ritz next week to meet with hundreds of investors and
venture capitalists representing hundreds of millions _ if not
billions _ of dollars who are looking for promising start-ups.
(Kanell, Atlanta Journal-Constitution). 15.
</P>
