   UNDATED _ People most familiar with August Strindberg have a
head start with the new film ``Miss Julie.'' Admirers of director
Mike Figgis will probably also be pleased. For everyone else,
though, ``Miss Julie'' will be a slow, grim sit. By ROBERT PHILPOT.
Story has moved in ``e'' entertainment category. &QL; 
 &QL; 
 &QL;
